    <!-- Introduction -->
    <section class="section">
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>The flexibility and adaptability of a management application largely depend on how its settings can be configured. With this in mind, <strong>Movelys integrates a comprehensive, structured, and highly customizable</strong> settings module, allowing each company to tailor the tool to its specific operational, legal, and commercial needs.</p>
        
        <p>The settings module acts as the <strong>system's configuration hub, providing a centralized interface</strong> to define the fundamental rules of the application. It allows for configuring general company information (company name, logo, contact details, currencies, date and time formats), tax preferences, units of measurement, payment methods, tax rates, languages, printing preferences, invoicing options, and many other essential elements.</p>
        
        <p>Thanks to this fine-grained configuration, Movelys ensures global consistency, local regulatory compliance (especially for tax aspects), and advanced customization of the user experience. Administrators thus have full control over the elements structuring their team's work environment while ensuring better integration of modules (sales, purchases, products, inventory, reports, etc.).</p>
    </section>

