    </tr>
</table>
        
<p><strong>Example: A barcode 2 0 0 1 2 3 0 0 4 5 0 0 can be interpreted as follows:</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li>2 0 = prefix</li>
    <li>0 1 2 3 0 = product ID (5 digits)</li>
    <li>0 4 5 0 0 = weight 4.500 kg (4 digits for whole, 3 for decimal)</li>
</ul>
        
